      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence and round-off error must be characterized and shown to be negligible relative to discretization error for hemolysis QoI.",
      "rationale": "Iterative convergence monitored via residual norms but formal solver error quantification per ASME V&V 20 was not performed. Factor flagged as not-assessed; achieved level set to 1 as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Evidence of independent simulation review, analyst qualification records, and documented simulation plan must be provided.",
      "rationale": "No independent review of simulation setup documented. Analyst qualifications not formally recorded in the credibility evidence package. Factor not-assessed at MRL 5."
    },
