      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model input parameters must be traceable to measured data or published literature with uncertainty bounds. Input uncertainty must be propagated through the model.",
      "rationale": "Blood viscosity and density sourced from literature with wide inter-study ranges. Hematocrit assumed constant at 40% without distribution. Monte Carlo propagation performed for six parameters but input uncertainty bounds are not fully justified from primary measurement data. Achieved level 2."
